      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAMACRI (2) has been in the top four at all five runs this prep, the latest offering a fast-finishing second over 1300m at Dubbo. Needs the extra trip now. On a nine-day back-up and won't get a better chance to break a 506-day win drought. DEODEE (1) returned from an eight-month spell with an eye-catching third last time out after missing the start over 1100m at Dubbo. Will relish the extra ground today. Drawn to enjoy an economical run and is sure to prove tough to hold out. MOON ZONE (5) improved significantly when second-up from a spell recently, chiming in late to finish a close fourth over 1200m at this track. An extra 200m at this stage of the prep is the perfect scenario. RUBY HARMONY (3) hasn't landed a blow in two runs this prep over shorter trips. Might be worth one more chance out to 1400m. EPIC STATEMENT (7) struggled over the mile here last time out. Can improve in this more suitable contest.",
